# HTML UI

Pages: `index.html` (auth), `account.html` (hub), `fantasy_draft_2026.html` (draft), `1_league_setup.html` (offline setup).

## Style

- Dark theme, system font stack, CSS variables where present (`--bg`, `--surface`, `--accent`)
- Inline `<style>` blocks and inline `onclick` handlers — match surrounding file, do not introduce React/Vue
- Tables/grids: explicit `grid-template-columns`, position color classes (`.QB`, `.RB`, `.WR`, `.TE`)

## UI rules

- Keep dense draft info scannable: rank, VORP, ADP delta, position badge
- Modals for Sleeper connect, mock draft, trades, draft report — follow existing overlay pattern
- Do not extract shared CSS unless requested; consistency within each file first

## Script loading

- Draft page: Supabase CDN + `draft_app.js`
- Auth pages: Supabase CDN only (inline auth scripts)
